# PDF Export Rules

PDF export must follow `pdf_export.spec.json`.

## Requirements
- Includes: cover, exec summary, phase 1–5, action plan.
- Charts: prefer SVG export; fallback to images if needed.
- Kanban/Boards must be flattened to tables for PDF.

## Jobs
- Export runs as a job (`pdf_export_job`) with statuses queued/running/done/failed.
- UI shows progress and provides download link when ready.

## Do Not
- Do not change section order or omit required sections from spec.
